        <Parent_String>Vinca (style and culture) [300019344], European Neolithic (culture or period) [300019332], ancient European styles and periods [300019281], Early Western World [300019255], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
